Step 1:
Store this file with necessary changes on JumpHost.

Step 2:
apply this command.
$ kubectl apply -f file.yml

Step 3:
to check if all is working fine , execute this command.
$ kubectl exec envars-fieldref -c fieldref-container -n fieldref-namespace -- printenv NODE_NAME POD_IP POD_NAME POD_NAMESPACE POD_SERVICE_ACCOUNT
